               <msContents>
                  <summary>Contract for the sale of 6 2/3 arourae of catoecic land in the Oxyrhynchite nome for 1000 drachmae, the seller being Aphroditous, a freedwoman, acting with her husband Adrastus, and the buyer being Flavius Apion.  The adoptive mother of the seller, Thaisous, who seems to have had some rights of ownership over the land, appends her consent.</summary>
